title: Ronny Jackson
deleted: In 2018, a document containing more than 20 interviews conducted by staffers with people who served with Jackson alleged he “got drunk and wrecked a government vehicle” after a party and described “at least one occasion [when] Dr Jackson could not be reached when needed because he was passed out drunk in his hotel room”.<ref>{{cite news |last1=Jacobs |first1=Ben |title=Ronny Jackson crashed car while drunk and mishandled drugs, document claims |url=https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2018/apr/25/ronny-jackson-crashed-car-while-drunk-and-mishandled-drugs-document-shows |work=The Guardian |date=25 April 2018}}</ref>
